ISRAELI PERIODICALS AND SERIALS IN ENGLISH AND OTHER EUROPEAN LANGUAGES,
1974-78' A CLASSIFIED BIBLIOGRAPHY.
     
AN UPDATE TO THE AUTHOR'S BIBLIOGRAPHY IN 2ISRAELI PERIODICALS AND SERIALS IN
ENGLISH AND OTHER EUROPEAN LANGUAGES1 (SCARECROW PRESS, 1974) WITH ENTRIES FOR
434 SERIALS STARTED SINCE OR OMITTED FROM THE BIBLIOGRAPHY AND DETAILS OF
ABOUT 50 MENTIONED IN THE BIBLIOGRAPHY WHICH HAVE CHANGED OR DISAPPEARED.
